SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT BPIV_INVO_NO, BPIV_AMOUNTCURRINV, INVO_CURRENCY FROM :1/INVO INNER JOIN :1/BPIV ON INVO_NO = BPIV_INVO_NO WHERE BPIV_INVO_NO = :2 AND INVO_SCHEDULEDATE <= ':3' AND (INVO_FINALPAYMENTDATE > ':3' OR INVO_FINALPAYMENTDATE IS NULL) AND BPIV_CASHREPORTDATE <= ':3' AND NOT (BPIV_BTCH_BATCHCODE =':4' AND BPIV_BTPC_LINENO = 2) FOR FETCH ONLY
